\c 4
\s Mufananidzo wemukushi
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakatangazve kudzidzisa pagungwa; kukaungana kwaari chaunga chikuru zvekuti wakapinda muchikepe akagara mugungwa; uye chaunga chese chakange chiri pagungwa panyika.
\p
\v 2 Akavadzidzisa zvinhu zvizhinji nemifananidzo, akati kwavari padzidziso yake:
\v 3 Teererai; tarirai, mukushi wakabuda kunokusha.
\v 4 Zvino zvakaitika pakukusha, imwe yakawira parutivi rwenzira; shiri dzekudenga dzikauya dzikaidya dzikaipedza.
\v 5 Asi imwe yakawira panzvimbo dzine mabwe, payakange isina ivhu zhinji; pakarepo ikamera, nekuti yakange isina udziku hwevhu;
\v 6 asi zuva rakati rabuda, yakapiswa, uye nekuti yakange isina mudzi ikasvava.
\v 7 Uye imwe yakawira pamhinzwa, mhinzwa ikakura ikaivhunga, ikasabereka chibereko.
\v 8 Uye imwe yakawira muvhu rakanaka; ikabereka chibereko chakakura ikawedzera, ikabereka, imwe makumi matatu, neimwe makumi matanhatu, neimwe zana.
\v 9 Ndokuti kwavari: Une nzeve dzekunzwa, ngaanzwe.
\v 10 Zvino wakati ava oga, vakange vakamukomba nevanegumi nevaviri vakamubvunza zvemufananidzo.
\v 11 Uye akati kwavari: Kwamuri kwakapiwa kuziva chakavanzika cheushe hwaMwari; asi kuna avo vari kunze, zvose zvinoitwa nemifananidzo;
\v 12 kuti vachiona vaone asi varege kuonesesa, vachinzwa vanzwe asi vasinganzwisisi, zvimwe chero nguva varege kutendeuka, vakangamwirwe zvivi.
\p
\v 13 Zvino akati kwavari: Hamuzivi mufanandizo uyu here? Zvino muchaziva sei mifananidzo yose?
\v 14 Mukushi unokusha shoko.
\v 15 Zvino ava ndivo vaparutivi rwenzira, apo panokushwa shoko, uye kana vachirinzwa, pakarepo Satani unouya ndokubvisa shoko rakakushwa mumoyo yavo.
\v 16 Uye saizvozvo ava ndivo vakakushwa panzvimbo dzine mabwe, ivo kana vanzwa shoko, pakarepo vanorigamuchira nemufaro,
\v 17 asi havana mudzi mavari, asi ndevenguva; pashure kana matambudziko nekushushwa zvichiuya nekuda kweshoko, pakarepo vanogumburwa.
\v 18 Zvino ava ndivo vanokushwa mumhinzwa, vanonzwa shoko,
\v 19 asi kuzvidya moyo kwe\add zve\add*nyika ino nekunyengera kwefuma neruchiva pamusoro pezvimwe zvinhu zvichipinda, zvichivhunga shoko, rova risingabereki.
\v 20 Naava ndivo vakakushwa muvhu rakanaka, ndivo vanonzwa shoko, ndokugamuchira, vagobereka chibereko, umwe makumi matatu, uye umwe makumi matanhatu, uye umwe zana.
\s Mufananidzo womwenje
\p
\v 21 Zvino wakati kwavari: Mwenje unouiswa kuti uiswe pasi pedengu kana pasi pemubhedha here? Kwete kuti uiswe pachigadziko chemwenje here?
\v 22 Nekuti hapana chakavigwa chisingazovhundunurwi, kana chakachengetwa chakavanda, asi kuti zvibude pachena.
\v 23 Kana munhu ane nzeve dzekunzwa, ngaanzwe.
\v 24 Zvino wakati kwavari: Chenjererai zvamunonzwa; nechiyero chamunoyera nacho chichayerwa kwamuri, nekwamuri imwi munonzwa, chichawedzerwa.
\v 25 Nekuti ani nani unacho uchapiwa; asi usina uchatorerwa kunyange nechaanacho.
\s Kukura kweushe hwekudenga
\p
\v 26 Zvino akati: Hwakadaro ushe hwaMwari, sezvinonzi munhu unokusha mbeu muvhu.
\v 27 Zvino ovata nekumuka usiku nemasikati, mbeu inomera ichikura iye asingazivi kuti sei.
\v 28 Nekuti ivhu rinozviberekera chibereko pacharo, pakutanga chipande, pashure hura, pashure zviyo zvakakora pahura.
\v 29 Asi kana chibereko chaibva, pakarepo unotuma jeko nekuti kukohwa kwasvika.
\s Mufananidzo wembeu yemasitadha*
\p
\v 30 Zvino wakati: Tichafananidza nei ushe hwaMwari? Tingahuenzanisa nemuenzaniso upi?
\v 31 Setsanga yemasitadha*, iyo kana ichidzvarwa muvhu, idukusa kumbeu dzose dzepanyika;
\v 32 asi kana yadzvarwa, inokura ichiva huru kumirivo yose, ichiita matavi makuru zvekuti shiri dzekudenga dzinogona kuvakira pamumvuri wawo.
\p
\v 33 Zvino nemifananidzo mizhinji yakadaro, akataura shoko kwavari, sepavaigona kunzwa napo.
\v 34 Asi kunze kwemifananidzo haana kutaura kwavari; asi vava vega, wakadudzira vadzidzi vake zvose.
\s Jesu unonyaradza dutu remhepo
\p
\v 35 Zvino nezuva iroro ava madekwana, wakati kwavari: Ngatiyambukire mhiri.
\v 36 Vakarega chaunga chichiinda, vakaenda naye akangodaro muchikepe. Zvino kwaivawo nemamwe magwa naye.
\v 37 Zvino kwakamuka dutu guru remhepo, mafungu akazviroverera muchikepe, zvekuti chakange zvino chozadzwa.
\v 38 Asi iye wakange ari shure muchikepe avete pamutsago; vakamumutsa, vakati kwaari: Mudzidzisi, hamuna hanya kuti toparara here?
\v 39 Akamuka akatsiura mhepo, akati kugungwa: Nyarara, gadzikana! Mhepo ikamira, kukava nekudzikama kukuru.
\v 40 Ndokuti kwavari: Munotyirei zvakadaro? Hamuna rutendo sei?
\v 41 Vakatya nekutya kukuru, vakati umwe kune umwe: Zvino ndiani uyu, kuti kunyange mhepo negungwa zvinomuteerera?
